Titolo: Far Cry Vengeance

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: Far Cry Vengeance is a 2006 first-person shooter game developed by Ubisoft Montreal and published by Ubisoft for the Wii. Vengeance is a remake of Far Cry Instincts: Evolution, the previous Xbox title, and features three new levels, new weapons, vehicles, and controls.
The game received largely negative reviews upon release with criticism for the graphics, overly compressed FMVs, and poor enemy AI, though the controls were praised.